Description: ===================
        django-private-chat
        ===================
        
        .. image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/django-private-chat.svg
            :target: https://badge.fury.io/py/django-private-chat
        
        .. image:: https://travis-ci.org/Bearle/django-private-chat.svg?branch=master
